close_reason: "Delivered and maintained by pm-ugqx: SDK define/compose/testing builders, extension runtime, 11 packages, and plugin integrations."
body: "## Agent need\npm is a universal PM tool that ships primitives via an SDK, so any project can extend it (custom commands, types, search, importers, hooks) without forking the core.\n\n## Delivered surface (pm-ugqx)\nsrc/sdk define/compose/runtime/testing; extension loader + registries; capability-usage least-privilege; 11 first-party packages as exemplars; pm-claude/pm-codex plugins.\n\n## Verified by\nScaffold capability matrix (9/9), sandbox tarball install tests (CJS + ESM). Enduring agent-value statement for the extension/SDK capability; new work lands in pm-ugqx."
